{"tid":602223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）【連累食客】同行相爭竟落毒！ 48人食「蔥肉餅」入院","createTime":"2018-03-23T00:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T02:16:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d99802af9836a72860681ab212b35069c456056","tid":602223,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T00:56:34.000Z","msg":"即時兩岸  2018-03-22 20:11:27 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n同行相爭，竟然連累食客！福建寧德市古田縣公安局官方微信今日通報稱，該縣鶴塘鎮13日發生的48人集體食物中毒事件，經調查確認，是因銷售光餅同業競爭引發的投放危險物質案件。<br />\n<br />\n通報指，事發當日，有當地人和過往旅客在古田縣鶴塘鎮坊下路口購買光餅食用後，出現嘔吐、麻痹等不良反應。截至15日凌晨零時，寧德市、古田縣醫院共收治疑似患者48人，其中住院治療41人（重症6人、中度9人、輕度26人）。經治療，所有病人情況穩定，並逐步恢復健康。<br />\n<br />\n通報續指，經寧德市產品質量檢驗所對送檢光餅樣品檢測，確認涉事光餅中的「蔥肉餅」鋇元素含量異常。調查後發現，經營者當日加工製作光餅約500塊，其中「蔥肉餅」數量約100塊。<br />\n<br />\n通報稱，涉嫌犯案的34歲張姓男子，目前已被古田縣公安局依法刑事拘留，案件正在進一步偵辦中。"},{"pid":"4d9d1b59c824f9ca519529c22bb4e84ded059cd1","tid":602223,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef1f47aa83103032c4abac80c09f9a00dca1a77","tid":602223,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:03:00.000Z","msg":"失手喎 毒唔死"},{"pid":"7adce409167d9fedf05f60b53eb01bbb2504e56b","tid":602223,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:09:21.000Z","msg":"冇死人<br />\n<br />\n毒就毒狠d啦，小朋友玩遊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1246a3674cff81edf9e7479824d22af3fcaa0f4a","tid":602223,"uid":19643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef1f47aa83103032c4abac80c09f9a00dca1a77","tid":602223,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:03:00.000Z","msg":"失手喎 毒唔死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"中國既毒藥係假"},{"pid":"1fddfd3fd9a159eb3ff59d477b9bdad93c0712c8","tid":602223,"uid":74334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:10:51.000Z","msg":"個凶手估唔到<br />\n連毒藥都係假既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca7b34bc305658bbb25bf9e8ea2866437a2a475","tid":602223,"uid":5159,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1246a3674cff81edf9e7479824d22af3fcaa0f4a","tid":602223,"uid":19643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef1f47aa83103032c4abac80c09f9a00dca1a77","tid":602223,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:03:00.000Z","msg":"失手喎 毒唔死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"中國既毒藥係假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:11:21.000Z","msg":"食客先係假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本中國人食乜野元素都唔會中毒"},{"pid":"16685c5f167e9cdfaae8da669facc0ec19e5ed65","tid":602223,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:16:40.000Z","msg":"邊個寫傢，寫得咁撚差，毒自己定毒人地？"}]}